Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't like three years ago.\NI've created a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.49,0:00:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I now have a country\Nto protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieselotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to abduct you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carmilla!\NThis is my way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My life was saved by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for you,\NI would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is to repay me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have gone to such \Nlengths just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not only for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not only for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... am in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Laugh at me if you like.\NI have only met you twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we haven't even spent an hour\Nin each other's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fell in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.01,0:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are very young, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen them in videos, but they're\Nquieter than I expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These use the Rave Engine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, are you sure about this?\NYour father, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure. We're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Walking away from such an\Nideal environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.96,0:04:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As researchers,\Nthey have a screw loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're swimming in research funding,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't have to obey \Nthe Healthcare Charter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we can experiment on all the\Nhuman test subjects we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'll let you\Nout later, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're Saki Rukino,\Nthe Valvrave pilot, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have more questions for you\Nthan I can possibly ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite formidable,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It took me 10 years\Nto come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only I were stronger,\NI could have—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Cain said it would\Nbe more fun over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.21,0:05:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doing as he said\Nwas totally the right call!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a knife fight.\NI haven't done that in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death to traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're being shelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've found us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by Dorssian forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did they know what\Nwe were up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've destroyed the runway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shuttle can't take \Noff without a runway!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They saw through\Nour entire plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had factored in the idea of using\Nthe shuttle at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather not destroy such\Na beautiful building, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahi and the guys have been spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe're not supposed to yet, but let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The fighting has started!\NThe time for hacking is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, L-elf!\NThis is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Q-vier is here,\Nthat Cain is, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In which case, he must already\Nknow about the shuttle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-neun turned traitor!\NJust like you, L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't put him\Nup to it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf! Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me!\NTake her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is about to become\Na battle against Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight that\Nwith a knife, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The bridge...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima, go to the museum!\NTake good care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. It looks like\NL-elf has a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The boy who is fighting\Nthe whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that organism?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Organism"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, this isn't the first\Ntime you've seen a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Human? No, that organism\Nis the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lifeform that has \Ntaken over a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lieselotte, I'm going to save you\Nfor sure this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All combat-capable squads,\Npursue L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without him, the enemy is nothing\Nbut a giant that has lost its brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain, what in \Nthe world is a Magius?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We Magiuses came to Earth\Nseveral hundred years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a freak accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We could not establish \Ncontact with our homeworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand had no means of getting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:10:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had simply been waiting for\Ndeath on this unknown planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but then we transferred ourselves\Ninto Earth's creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Body-jacking...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have no physical form,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we needed vessels, bodies, \Nto survive here on this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The same! The same!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were marooned here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just like us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kind seems to resemble us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NArtificially, I suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The real goal of the Valvraves is\Nto create a new form of life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! You have surpassed humanity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have survived all this \Ntime by passing from one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,human body to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're a super-old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otamaya, this thing is ready\Nto go at any time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Assuming we can get out the front\Ndoor in one piece, yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be destroyed\Nif we try to leave like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!\NLet's just surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it! Don't give up\Nuntil L-elf comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After a long, secret war against humanity,\Nwe created an organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A group founded by selecting the most\Ninfluential humans and Magiuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Its objective was to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hide the existence of \NMagiuses from the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to allow for our food needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Food"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only lifeform that possesses Runes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in large quantities here \Non Earth is humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I survive by devouring humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI am their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haruto! You okay?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yamada, I can't—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come inside for\Nthe time being, Tokishima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take turns to keep your\Nheat levels from rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inuzuka is here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he has the prisoners \Nthat they rescued!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Let's open the hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otamaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Impact Boosters' cooling\Nfins don't have enough cooling capacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're out of spares!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, they are vulnerable to heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we fly here on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we overheat in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They are the result of my refusing\Nthe Council of 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is my punishment for trying
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to reveal everything and find \Na way to coexist with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.02,0:14:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Runes are siphoned off\Nat regular intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It leaves me in a constant state\Nof barely clinging to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am grateful I had this \Nchance to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't fled with you, Michael\Nwouldn't have left either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then you did this for L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael said that he\Nwas in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I am a Magius.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot be with a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't arbitrarily write \Nit off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf wouldn't want that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and knowing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that he can make \Nboth you and himself happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so smart and level-headed that\Nit makes me mad. So please, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael is most fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He has a good friend in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, they won't stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, don't try to fly!\NIf you overheat, it's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already got bigger problems!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if all they do is\Nprovide cover, we'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We wait for instructions\Nfrom L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Professor Kibukawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.49,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the hangar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's running a check\Non the shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has Unit 1 returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes! But we're pinned down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Renbokoji. We're changing course.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave from the east side\Nand use the road as a runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't, there's a river to the east.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThere's not enough room to take off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I lower the drawbridge, it will link\Nto the road on the far side of the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How will you lower it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of something.\NJust carry out your instructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the area past\Nthe river safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a country road, but it will work.\NLet's have faith in L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's been a change in route.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:09.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We're using the road to \Nthe east as a runway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.40,0:17:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}L-elf will lower the drawbridge for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe'll use the road as our runway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it around!\NUnit 5, smash through the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf... You always\Nthink of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... what about Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've beaten you, Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The drawbridge is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's what he's planning...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf, you know this city like the\Nback of your hand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move! Can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can fly! I'm good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away\Nfrom us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Escape, Lieselotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of fool are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly how it feels\Nto want to save someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Löwenglitzen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\NThis thing's aim is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it did enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Output falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have enough thrust\Nto leave the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to explode!\NDetach us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! If we lose altitude now,\Nwe'll be shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you push it\Nwith Unit 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't, I'm already on the\Nverge of overheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Michael... I feel the same way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The curse of diffusion breakdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NBut that won't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the light of a Valvrave!\NIs there another unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:18.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It truly made me happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you said\Nyou loved me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are not physical beings,\Nbut rather spiritual ones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.94,Italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in spite of that, we \Nnever quite understood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhat the humans called "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:57.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...now, thanks to you,\NI feel as if I do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That light... It's Lieselotte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...love you... in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.87,0:24:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 20.\N"The Kamitsuki Exposed."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.44,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system that will expose \Nthe truth of the world.